===Noun===
{{en-noun-reg}}

# {{botany}} a [[seed]] case for legumes (i.e. peas, beans, peppers)
# (''collective'') a group of [[whale]]s, [[dolphin]]s, or [[porpoise]]s
# a small vehicle, especially used in emergency situations.

